title: The Door

description.plain: The Door is the follow-up single to Teddy Swims’ breakout hit Lose Control. It serves as the 3rd single from his debut album I’ve Tried Everything But Therapy Part 1. The lyrics tell the story of Swims leaving a toxic relationship so he can go back to focusing on himself and loving himself again. The song reached a peak of #24 on the Billboard Hot 100 on October 12th, 2024.
